---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
        <script id="mcjs">!function(c,h,i,m,p){m=c.createElement(h),p=c.getElementsByTagName(h)[0],m.async=1,m.src=i,p.parentNode.insertBefore(m,p)}(document,"script","https://chimpstatic.com/mcjs-connected/js/users/3c50af1876396b0b1f0998b9e/9e49d36f7ae0211192b8488d4.js");</script>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>Welcome to Serbia Shop!</h1>
    <p>
        Are you looking to expand your business horizons or start a new life in the Balkans? 
        We specialize in helping international entrepreneurs navigate **Business Formation** as the primary pathway to obtaining Serbian residency.
    </p>
    
    <p>
        Our streamlined approach covers everything from initial company registration to 
        the final approval of your residency permit, ensuring your business and legal 
        status are fully compliant with Serbian law.
    </p>

    <h2>Our Specialized Services:</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Business Formation:</strong> Full support for registering a limited liability company (DOO) or entrepreneur status (Preduzetnik).</li>
        <li><strong>Residency Applications:</strong> Expertise in residency based on business ownership, employment, or family reunification.</li>
        <li><strong>Legal & Tax Consultation:</strong> Guidance on local tax obligations and banking for new international residents.</li>
        <li><strong>Administrative Handling:</strong> We manage your translations, notary appointments, and all interactions with the Ministry of Interior.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
        Start your business journey in Serbia today. We provide the local expertise 
        necessary to turn your relocation goals into reality.
    </p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
